==Korean==

===Etymology===

From [[북방]] (''buk.bang'', "northern") + [[긴]] (''gin'', adjective form of [[길다]], "to be long") + [[수염]] (''su.yeom'', "whisker") + [[고래]] (''go.rae'', "whale") 

===Noun===

'''북방긴수염고래''' (buk.bang.gin.su.yeom.go.rae)

# Pacific Northern [[right whale]], ''[[Eubalaena japonica]]''.

